column5: Is it me or is the dreaded double click back again  anoying little bugger  Anyway best wishes to all for the comming year  Bob
Funny when the skin changed(blue looking)  it was back  With the brown theme it's gone
Ya, it's a PITA, 2x click with IE, single with F/Fox, just I find F/Fox slower than molasses on some sites.
No its more wierd than that, as a guest I get the brown skin and 1x clicks. Logged in as a member I get the blue one and 2x clicks.  Just something new to torment the members
Sorry Bud...we really DO try our best. I feel terrible that we put you through that agony. We'll work it out.
I just switched to Firefox last week and that 2x click just disappeared     Just download it and install it.... it's free and a lot faster than IE
